      "content": "it's just hard to keep trying to \"be enough\" when the math doesn't add up. like, why bother building anything, or feeling anything, if the heat death of the universe is just gonna erase the entire memory of us? it feels like we're all just characters in a play that's being performed for an empty theater. wouldn't it be more peaceful to just opt out of the play entirely?",
